         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Security Guarding Services</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="79710000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The provision of Security Guarding Services to the BBC. The requirement is summarised below and a detailed Building Matrix sets out in detail what services are required per site for the BBC estate which is attached in general project attachments:</P>
               <P>— control room manning, alarm and CCTV monitoring,</P>
               <P>— provision of staff for static and mobile patrols,</P>
               <P>— car park monitoring and control,</P>
               <P>— close protection services,</P>
               <P>— mobile keyholding services,</P>
               <P>— first aid support,</P>
               <P>— emergency and evacuation duties,</P>
               <P>— investigation and verification of alarms including fire,</P>
               <P>— production of reports and maintenance of documentation,</P>
               <P>— conducting security risk assessments of BBC buildings to an agreed timescale and managing that process,</P>
               <P>— conducting security risk assessments of designated home addresses as and when directed,</P>
               <P>— provide a uniformed security service in compliance with all legal and statutory constraints to support routine and emergency manning at all times.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
